digiKam 2.1.0 - Release date: 2011-09-04

NEW FEATURES:

CameraGUI : camera items thumbnails are processed on the fly. Connection to camera device is faster.
CameraGUI : Sort of items by date is possible with photo taken quickly (less than 1s).
CameraGUI : New option to setup a default target album to download items from camera device.
CameraGUI : New option to download new items in just one click.
CameraGUI : New option to filter icon-view by type mime.

Preview   : New option to show/hide information over preview canvas.

